CPAN-Testers
============

DESCRIPTION

This distribution provides an overview of the CPAN Testers project, with
links to further resources to help you find out more or better still get you
involved as a CPAN Tester.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

 perl Makefile.PL
 make
 make test
 make install

However, this distribution is a collection of documents, rather than something
to install and use.

CHANGES

For a complete list of changes, see the Changes file.

SUPPORT

There are no known typos, errors or bugs at the time of this release. However, 
if you spot any inaccuracies, please submit a bug to the RT system. It would 
also help greatly if you are able to pinpoint problems or even supply a patch. 

Fixes are dependent upon their severity and our availability. Should a fix not
be forthcoming, please feel free to (politely) remind us.

RT: http://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=CPAN-Testers

